official_title: Feasibility and Evaluation of a Self-care App to Enhance Purposeful Living
inclusion_criteria:
* Diagnosis of ovarian cancer or treatment for ovarian cancer through the University of Michigan Gynecologic Oncology service
* Completed primary treatment (either surgery alone or surgery + chemotherapy)
* Ability to understand and the willingness to sign a written informed consent
* Ability to speak and read English
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 18 Years
exclusion_criteria: * There are no additional exclusion criteria for participation in this study.
